        "title": "Improve Traditional Chinese localization wording",
        "body": "## Summary\n- Refine Traditional Chinese localization wording for more natural Taiwan usage.\n- Replace provider terminology from 供應商 to 提供者 across zh-Hant strings.\n- Localize CodexBar notification copy for quota warnings, session depleted/restored, and login success.\n\n## Root Cause\n- Settings notification labels were localized, but posted `UNMutableNotificationContent` title/body strings still used hardcoded English.\n\n## Visual Proof\n- Redacted zh-Hant app screenshots showing Traditional Chinese strings loaded in the running app.\n- The proof covers General, Providers, About, and Debug settings panes. Cost, plan, cookie source, build timestamp, and local path details are redacted.\n\n### General\n<img width=\"1122\" height=\"1402\" alt=\"General settings in Traditional Chinese\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/f37c300f-4dd6-4a57-8eeb-e12afe34b483\" />\n\n### Providers\n<img width=\"1296\" height=\"1214\" alt=\"Providers settings in Traditional Chinese\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/b2390190-8d78-46a7-83c3-1a4b75c9034a\" />\n\n### About\n<img width=\"1116\" height=\"1409\" alt=\"About settings in Traditional Chinese\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/a762b177-f347-41af-b6b2-cfa3bf3bc478\" />\n\n### Debug\n<img width=\"1124\" height=\"1399\" alt=\"Debug settings in Traditional Chinese\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/16056182-512f-4e1d-bdae-37d2d6f82867\" />\n\n## Validation\n- `make check`\n- `swift test --filter 'QuotaWarningNotificationLogicTests|SessionQuotaNotificationLogicTests|LoginNotificationLogicTests|LocalizationBundleTests'`\n- `plutil -lint Sources/CodexBar/Resources/*/Localizable.strings`\n- placeholder parity check between en and zh-Hant strings\n- `git diff --check HEAD`",
